---
title: Spicy Prawn Burger with paprika baby potatoes
description: Sandwiched between the soft and slightly sweet brioche buns in this recipe, you'll find juicy prawns, spicy carrot slaw, pickled onion and fresh tomatoes. A vibrant salad and buttery paprika potatoes round out a pleasing plate that's nothing short of great!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R15_W33_IE_IECS23228-2_Main_F1_Version2_high-4be0780f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/664f2d2c8606e082f1887767-en-IE.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipes/spicy-prawn-burger-664f2d2c8606e082f1887767
